# Import HLA loci alignment stats from arcas logs
hla_mapping_stats_import <- function(samples, log_dir){
  tibble(sample = samples) %>% 
    mutate(data = map(sample, function(x){
      log_path <- sprintf("%s/%s.genotype.log",log_dir,x)
      df <- tibble(lines = read_lines(log_path))
      if (any(grepl("error", df$lines, ignore.case = T))){
        NA
      } else {
        df %>% 
          mutate(lines = gsub("\t", "", lines)) %>% 
          filter(grepl("^HLA", lines)) %>% 
          separate(lines, into = c("locus", "abundance", "reads", "classes"), sep = " +")
      }
    })) %>%
    unnest(data) %>% 
    select(!(contains("data"))) %>% 
    separate(locus, into = c(NA, "locus"), sep = "-")
}
alignment_stats_bulk_df <- hla_mapping_stats_import(samples_bulk, arcas_log_bulk_dir)

pmid_sample_rename <- function(df){
  pmid_key <- suppressMessages(read_csv("/labs/khatrilab/solomonb/covid/pmid30518681/pmid30518681_samples.csv") %>% 
    select(sample_name = sample, run_name = Run))
  name_check <- any(df$sample %in% pmid_key$sample_name)
  if (name_check){
    message("Names already formatted")
    return(df)
  }
  df %>% 
    left_join(pmid_key, c("sample" = "run_name")) %>% 
    select(-sample) %>% 
    rename("sample" = sample_name)
}

create_drb345_df <- function(ratio_df, copy_number_df){
  ratio_df %>% 
    pivot_wider(names_from = 'locus', values_from ='frequency', values_fill=0) %>% 
    left_join(copy_number_df, by = c('sample')) %>% 
    drop_na()
}
